a-label=\"3 of 4\" inert=\"true\" style=\"left: 200%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_DH_gemini-image__grounded-ima.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_DH_gemini-image__grounded-ima.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"A 16:9 aspect ratio image of Museum Clos Lucé rendered in the style of bright-colored Synthetic Cubism without any text\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_DH_gemini-image__grounded-ima.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-2\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"whck6\">Museum Clos Lucé in Synthetic Cubism style</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1772121752673-3\" aria-label=\"4 of 4\" inert=\"true\" style=\"left: 300%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_gemini-image_localisation_1_l.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_gemini-image_localisation_1_l.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"2 images on a white background: First, A cinematic close-up of an intricately illustrated sign made of recycled material featuring local birds and flowers and text that reads &quot;Native Wildlife: Please Observe from a Distance&quot; against a soft blur of green foliage.  Second, a version of the &quot;Native Wildlife&quot; sign localized for an Indian setting, with all text translated into Hindi\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_gemini-image_localisation_1_l.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-3\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"whck6\">Localized \"Native Wildlife\" sign</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752673-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752673-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752673-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752673-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Nano Banana 2: Combining Pro capabilities with lightning\\u002Dfast speed&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"rpgki\"><i>Read the prompts: Water Cycle</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-1\" id=\"footnote-source-1\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 1\"> <sup>1</sup> </a> <i>, Cloud Infographic</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-2\" id=\"footnote-source-2\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 2\"> <sup>2</sup> </a> <i>, Cubism</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-3\" id=\"footnote-source-3\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 3\"> <sup>3</sup> </a> <i>, Wildlife Sign</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-4\" id=\"footnote-source-4\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 4\"> <sup>4</sup> </a></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Nano Banana 2: Combining Pro capabilities with lightning\\u002Dfast speed&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"zfhnu\">Enhanced creative control</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"99rmq\">Nano Banana 2 also dramatically closes the gap between speed and visual fidelity, delivering high-quality, photorealistic imagery. Here’s what our newest model offers and has improved on from the original Nano Banana:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ev6k6\"><b>Subject consistency:</b> Maintain character resemblance of up to five characters and the fidelity of up to 14 objects in a single workflow, allowing you to storyboard and build narratives without altering the appearance of your inputs.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"51n8g\"><b>Precise instruction following:</b> With enhanced instruction following, the model adheres more strictly to your complex requests, capturing the specific nuances of your idea so the image you get is the image you asked for.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"9tvr\"><b>Production-ready specs</b>: Make attention grabbing assets with full control of various aspect ratios and resolutions from 512px to 4K, ensuring your visuals stay sharp whether they are for a vertical social post or a wide-screen backdrop.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"1l1m9\"><b>Visual fidelity upgrade:</b> Nano Banana 2 delivers vibrant lighting, richer textures and sharper details, maintaining high-quality aesthetics at the speed expected from Flash.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"Nano Banana 2: Combining Pro capabilities with lightning\\u002Dfast speed\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/gemini-image__subject-consist.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/gemini-image__subject-consist.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &q