 <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-3\" data-index=\"4\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 4</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Nano Banana 2: Combining Pro capabilities with lightning\\u002Dfast speed&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <p data-block-key=\"rpgki\"><i>Read the prompts: Farm</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-5\" id=\"footnote-source-5\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 5\"> <sup>5</sup> </a> <i>, Treehouse</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-6\" id=\"footnote-source-6\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 6\"> <sup>6</sup> </a> <i>, Valley</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-7\" id=\"footnote-source-7\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 7\"> <sup>7</sup> </a> <i>, Portrait</i> <a class=\"superscript\" data-ga4-analytics-superscript-click=\"\" data-target=\"inline text\" href=\"#footnote-8\" id=\"footnote-source-8\" aria-label=\"Jump to link reference 8\"> <sup>8</sup> </a></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Nano Banana 2: Combining Pro capabilities with lightning\\u002Dfast speed&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"zfhnu\">Try Nano Banana 2 today</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"5pcr1\">Whatever your needs, we now offer the perfect tool for every workflow: Nano Banana Pro for high-fidelity tasks requiring maximum factual accuracy, or Nano Banana 2 for rapid generation, precise instruction following and integrated image-search grounding.</p>\n     <p data-block-key=\"e863q\">Nano Banana 2 is rolling out today across Google products, including:</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li data-block-key=\"akajf\"><b>Gemini app:</b> Nano Banana 2 will replace Nano Banana Pro across the Fast, Thinking and Pro models. Google AI Pro and Ultra subscribers will keep access to Nano Banana Pro for specialized tasks by <a href=\"https://support.google.com/gemini/answer/14286560\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">regenerating images</a> via the three-dot menu.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"d25l0\"><b>Search:</b> In AI Mode and Lens, through the Google app as well as mobile and desktop browsers. View <a href=\"https://support.google.com/websearch/answer/16649374\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">availability here</a>, including 141 new countries and territories and eight additional languages.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"dgf4n\"><b>AI Studio + API:</b> Available in preview in <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/new_chat?model=gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AI Studio</a> and <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/image-generation\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Gemini API</a>. Pricing <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/pricing#gemini-3.1-flash-image-preview\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>. Also available in <a href=\"https://antigravity.google/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Antigravity</a>.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"ddqm3\"><b>Google Cloud:</b> Available in preview with the Gemini API in <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/vertex-ai?e=48754805\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Vertex AI</a>.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"b0emv\"><b>Flow:</b> Nano Banana 2 is the new default image generation model in <a href=\"https://flow.google/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Flow</a>, available to all Flow users for zero credits.</li>\n      <li data-block-key=\"fbot7\"><b>Ads:</b> Nano Banana is available in Ads, powering suggestions while creating campaigns.</li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <uni-image-carousel section-header=\"Nano Banana 2: Combining Pro capabilities with lightning\\u002Dfast speed\" images=\"[\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Gemini_Features_NB_Inline_202.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Gemini_Features_NB_Inline_202.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A user interface for the Gemini app template feature labeled, \\u0022Pick a style for your image.\\u0022 It shows a grid of 12 preview tiles with different artistic styles like \\u0022Monochrome,\\u0022 \\u0022Gothic clay,\\u0022 and \\u0022Steampunk,\\u0022 above a text prompt box that says \\u0022Describe your image.\\u0022&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/16_9.max-1600x1600.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/16_9.max-2160x2160.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A side\\u002Dby\\u002Dside comparison of two graphite pencil sketches showing different interpretations of a pufferfish nest: one a less accurate, textured, shell\\u002Dlined crater and the other a more accurate geometric, scientific diagram in a field notebook with handwritten annotations.&quot;,\n        &quot;isVideo&quot;: false,\n        &quot;autoplay&quot;: true,\n        &quot;videoTitle&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;audioDescriptiveVideoURL&quot;: &quot;&quot;,\n        &quot;videoTracks&quot;: [\n          \n        ]\n      },\n    \n      {\n        \n          \n          \n          &quot;src&quot;: [&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/NB2_Asset.max-1070x1070.format-webp.webp&quot;,&quot;https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/NB2_Asset.max-1070x1070.format-webp.webp&quot;],\n        \n        &quot;alt&quot;: &quot;A four\\u002Dpanel collage featu