 id=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-0\" aria-label=\"1 of 3\" style=\"left: 0%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_Gemini_Features_NB_Inline_202.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 800w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_Gemini_Features_NB_Inline_202.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"A user interface for the Gemini app template feature labeled, &quot;Pick a style for your image.&quot; It shows a grid of 12 preview tiles with different artistic styles like &quot;Monochrome,&quot; &quot;Gothic clay,&quot; and &quot;Steampunk,&quot; above a text prompt box that says &quot;Describe your image.&quot;\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_Gemini_Features_NB_Inline_202.max-1080x1080.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-0\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"60ul0\">Try Nano Banana 2 in the Gemini app, using the new templates feature.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-1\" aria-label=\"2 of 3\" inert=\"true\" style=\"left: 100%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_16_9.max-1600x1600.format-webp.webp 800w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_16_9.max-2160x2160.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"A side-by-side comparison of two graphite pencil sketches showing different interpretations of a pufferfish nest: one a less accurate, textured, shell-lined crater and the other a more accurate geometric, scientific diagram in a field notebook with handwritten annotations.\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_16_9.max-1600x1600.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-1\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"szo5t\">World knowledge from Nano Banana 2 in AI Mode in Search.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <div class=\"article-carousel__slide\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" id=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-2\" aria-label=\"3 of 3\" inert=\"true\" style=\"left: 200%;\">\n       <figure>\n        <div class=\"article-carousel__image-wrapper\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <img sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 32px), (min-width: 768px and max-width: 1024px) 800px, 565px\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"article-carousel__img\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_NB2_Asset.max-1070x1070.format-webp.webp 800w, https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_NB2_Asset.max-1070x1070.format-webp.webp 1600w\" alt=\"A four-panel collage featuring a whimsical kangaroo on vacation: steering a small blue boat at sea, sipping espresso at a Parisian cafe, lounging in a white bathrobe on a bed, and jumping in a colorful bouncy castle.\" src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260227091057_NB2_Asset.max-1070x1070.format-webp.webp\">\n        </div>\n        <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n        <figcaption class=\"article-carousel__caption\">\n         <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n         <div slot=\"caption-slot-2\" style=\"display: block;\">\n          <div class=\"rich-text\">\n           <p data-block-key=\"szo5t\">Subject preservation from Nano Banana 2 in Flow.</p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </figcaption>\n       </figure>\n      </div>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n     <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n     <div class=\"article-carousel__navigation ga4-bullets\" role=\"tablist\">\n      <!--?lit$6598226066$-->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button article-carousel__navigation-button--active\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-0\" data-index=\"1\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 1</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-1\" data-index=\"2\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 2</button>\n      <!---->\n      <!---->\n      <button class=\"article-carousel__navigation-button\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" aria-controls=\"carousel-item-1772121752674-2\" data-index=\"3\"><!--?lit$6598226066$-->Jump to position 3</button>\n      <!---->\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </uni-image-carousel>\n  <div class=\"module--text module--text__article\" role=\"presentation\" data-analytics-module=\"{\n           &quot;module_name&quot;: &quot;Paragraph&quot;,\n           &quot;section_header&quot;: &quot;Nano Banana 2: Combining Pro capabilities with lightning\\u002Dfast speed&quot;\n         }\">\n   <div class=\"uni-paragraph article-paragraph\" data-component=\"uni-article-paragraph\" data-component-initialized=\"true\">\n    <div class=\"rich-text\">\n     <h2 data-block-key=\"socl3\">Robust provenance: marking and verification</h2>\n     <p data-block-key=\"6jib\">As generative media evolves, so must the tools we use to identify and understand it. We continue to deepen our provenance approach, by coupling our state-of-the-art <a href=\"https://deepmind.google/models/synthid/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SynthID</a> technology with interoperable <a href=\"https://c2pa.org/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">C2PA Content Credentials</a>, we provide users with a more holistic and contextual view of not just if AI was used, but how.\n      <br>\n      <br>\n      Our provenance tools are already making an impact. Since its launch in November, our <a href=\"https://blog.google/innovation-and-ai/products/ai-image-verification-gemini-app/\">SynthID verification feature</a> in Gemini app has been used over 20 million times across various languages, helping people identify Google AI-generated images, video and audio. We’ll soon be bringing C2PA verification to the Gemini app, too.<span class=\"tombstone\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google DeepMind 发布 Nano Banana 2 (Gemini 3.1 Flash Image)，这是一款具备搜索增强世界知识和先进主体一致性的高速图像生成模型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google DeepMind 发布 Nano Banana 2 (Gemini 3.1 Flash Image)，这是一款具备搜索增强世界知识和先进主体一致性的高速图像生成模型。",
  "summary": "Google DeepMind 推出了 Nano Banana 2，亦被称为 Gemini 3.1 Flash Image。该模型旨在以 Flash 架构极快的速度提供 Pro 级别的先进推理能力和视觉质量。关键技术亮点包括集成实时网络搜索以实现图像的事实溯源、改进的文本渲染与本地化，以及在多次生成中保持多达 5 个角色一致性的能力。该模型支持高达 4K 的分辨率，并正被集成到 Google 的生态系统中，包括 Gemini 应用、搜索和 Vertex AI。此外，文章还强调了通过 SynthID 水印和 C2PA 元数据实现的安全性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Nano Banana 2 将 Pro 级别的智能引入高速 Flash 架构，在不牺牲视觉保真度的前提下实现快速迭代。",
      "explanation": "通过将 Gemini Pro 系列的推理能力集成到优化的 Flash 模型中，Google 使开发者能够以更低的延迟生成高质量图像，弥合了创意控制与生产速度之间的差距。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该模型利用实时网络搜索来准确渲染特定主体，并创建具有事实依据的信息图表和图表。",
      "explanation": "与传统的静态模型不同，Nano Banana 2 利用 Gemini 的现实世界知识库和实时网络搜索数据，提高了数据可视化和本地化文本渲染等复杂视觉任务的准确性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "它可以保持多达 5 个角色的相似度和 14 个物体的保真度，助力复杂的叙事故事板创作。",
      "explanation": "这一功能解决了 AI 图像生成中常见的主体偏移限制。通过确保跨多个帧的角色和物体一致性，该模型成为了专业故事板和长篇视觉叙事的实用工具。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Nano Banana 2 将 Gemini Flash 的高速智能引入视觉生成，使快速编辑和迭代成为可能。",
    "在单个工作流中保持多达 5 个角色的相似度和多达 14 个物体的保真度，让你能够创作故事板并构建叙事。",
    "该模型从 Gemini 的现实世界知识库中提取信息，并由来自网络搜索的实时信息和图像驱动，从而更准确地渲染特定主体。",
    "随着生成式媒体的发展，我们用于识别和理解它的工具也必须随之进化。我们通过将先进的 SynthID 技术与可互操作的 C2PA 内容凭证相结合，继续深化我们的溯源方法。"
  ],
